column2: SELECT top #   m.id AS id,   m.ra AS ra1, m.dec AS de1,    galex.ra AS galex_ra, galex.dec  AS galex_dec,    galex.e_bv  AS galex_e_bv,    galex.fuv_mag AS fuv_mag,  galex.fuv_magerr AS fuv_magerr,    galex.nuv_mag AS nuv_mag,  galex.nuv_magerr AS nuv_magerr,   galex.fuv_s2n AS fuv_s2n,  galex.nuv_s2n AS nuv_s2n FROM MyDB.irac2_corr AS m     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n     LEFT JOIN photoobjall AS galex ON n.objid=galex.objid
